Kitchen Gods is a 5-reel 3-row video slot with feature Wild Multiplier. The game is played with 50 credit for 243 ways to win. TOTAL BET = Credits x DENOM. DENOM is in range [$0.002, $0.006, $0.020, $0.040, $0.100, $0.200, $0.500, $1.000, $2.000]. Payouts are made according to the Paytable. Total winning = Total winning bet ways x Paytable x DENOM. All win shown in cash. Bet ways win if the winning symbols are in succession from the leftmost reel to the right. Only the highest win per bet way is paid. Total number of winning bet ways for each symbol are calculated by multiplying the number of adjacent winning symbols on each symbols from the leftmost reel to the right. Free Spin Feature is played at the same TOTAL BET as the spin that trigger the Free Spin Feature.
With Denom = $0.006 Total winning in this example: 2 x 1 x 3 x 15 x $0.006 = $0.540
